# Ephemeral plane (ADR-0002): the agent workspace — specs, work-plans,
# breakdowns. Never committed; committed ⇔ signed-off.
/.work/

# Agent skills: the engineering skill bodies are COMMITTED under .claude/skills/
# so a fresh clone has them with no install step. Ignore everything else under
# .claude/, the other agents' skill copies, and the superpowers cache.
/.claude/*
!/.claude/skills/
/.agents/
/.superpowers/
